Made for jon. I was gonna make a map for him eventually so here ya go. I was originally gonna make a bonus level but that's gonna be my next map. It'll be a recreation of the defrag map (from quake) called "lick-hq." I can't wait.

Difficulty: Hard - Extreme
Map time: 50s minimum (hopefully)
